      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question. i started this 10 day course of antibiotics for a skin infection a few days ago but the redness and swelling are totally gone now. i feel 100% fine. is it okay if i just stop taking them now so i dont have to deal with more meds? i dont really want to keep taking stuff i dont need.",
